<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Arbitration Process</span></p>
